            "answer": "That defeats the purpose. Your merchant account doesn't talk to our attribution system, rep wallets, or fraud protection the same way. Data gets lost. Attribution breaks. Reps don't get proper credit. We built this as one integrated system because partial implementations create expensive failures. We'd rather say no than help you recreate the same problems everyone else has."
